  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nThe delivery status of audio messages is stuck in a pending state (`...`) until reopening the chat (relevant for 1-1 chats, community channels, and group with members). After reopening, it's marked as `sent` or `delivered`, as expected. \r\nIn the case of a group chat, the issue is only reproducible for groups with joined members, i.e. if you create a group chat with no members and send an audio message, it'll be marked as `sent`. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe delivery status is updated without reopening the chat\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/172349367-6db427f6-8ca9-47a5-b315-0c495d620c63.MP4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Start a 1-1 chat\r\n2. Send an audio message\r\n3. Reopen the chat\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 7/06\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n[geth.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/8852118/geth.log)\r\n[Status.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/8852119/Status.log)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
